OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain,
OL,6,Fthis locally heavy. The rain breaking
OL,7,Finto showers, perhaps thundery during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Some brighter spells
OL,9,Fpossible later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FShowers easing during Monday and
OL,13,FTuesday with sunnier spells emerging.
OL,14,FSimilar on Wednesday with variable
OL,15,Famounts of cloud, feeling fresher than
OL,16,Frecent days as temperatures fall away.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
